OL,4,Cabandoned two cats in filthy home
OL,6,FA West Yorkshire man who left his home
OL,7,Fand abandoned his two cats in filthy
OL,8,Fconditions for nine days has been
OL,9,Fbanned from keeping animals for three
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,F23-year-old Reece Glossop from
OL,13,FWetherby left his pets Daisy and
OL,14,FMustafa without water and in a room
OL,15,Fstrewn with rubbish, faeces and mould.
OL,17,FGlossop told RSPCA inspectors who
OL,18,Fvisited his home that the animals were
OL,19,F'looking after themselves' whilst he
OL,20,Fhad been away.
