OL,3,CBan on keeping animals for man who
OL,4,Cabandoned two cats in filthy home
OL,6,FHe was sentenced for an offence under
OL,7,Fthe Animal Welfare Act at Bradford and
OL,8,FKeighley Magistrates' Court and was
OL,9,Fplaced on a 12 month community order
OL,10,Fin addition to the ban.
OL,12,FThe court heard how Glossop left his
OL,13,Fflat over Christmas and New Year and
OL,14,Fwhen he returned told inspectors that
OL,15,Fhe intended to clean his home.
OL,17,FWhen he returned home a second time
OL,18,Fthe flat was in the same condition.
